## VIII. 🌐 Google Flow Internal API — Cách Extension Tương Tác

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as 💉 Content Script
    participant UI as 🌐 Google Flow React UI
    participant API as 🔗 aisandbox-pa.googleapis.com
    participant INT as 🔓 MAIN World Interceptor

    Note over CS,API: ——— Phase 1: Setup & Input ———
    CS->>UI: querySelector('textarea') → setReactInputValue(prompt)
    CS->>UI: querySelector('[aria-label="16:9"]') → reactClick()
    CS->>UI: querySelector('button[Generate]') → reactClick()

    Note over CS,API: ——— Phase 2: Generation (30s - 5min) ———
    UI->>API: POST /v1/projects/{id}/generate\n{prompt, model: "veo-3.1", ratio: "16:9"}
    API-->>UI: {operationId: "op_xxx", state: "PROCESSING"}
    INT-->>CS: CustomEvent('__VEO_STATUS__', {state: "PROCESSING"})

    loop Poll mỗi 5 giây
        UI->>API: GET /v1/operations/op_xxx
        API-->>UI: {state: "PROCESSING", progress: 45}
        INT-->>CS: CustomEvent('__VEO_STATUS__', {progress: 45})
        CS->>CS: sendMessage(PROGRESS_UPDATE, 45%)
    end

    Note over CS,API: ——— Phase 3: Completion & Download ———
    API-->>UI: {state: "COMPLETED", downloadUrl: "https://...mp4"}
    INT-->>CS: CustomEvent('__VEO_VIDEO_URL__', {url: "https://...mp4"})
    CS-->>CS: Return {success: true, videoUrl}
    Note over CS: Service Worker calls chrome.downloads.download()
```

